<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="CH8x4309-en-f0676845" type="comment"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Comments to 算數書</title><editor role="creator">sin-aps Project</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="1">This work is in the public domain</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><p>Created by members of the TLS project</p><p>Comments and notes to <bibl corresp="#CH8x4309"><title xml:lang="och">算數書</title></bibl>for translation <ref target="#CH8x4309-en-37d7b93f"/>.</p></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#andrea.breard">Initially created: <date>2023-01-06T02:15:47.29+09:00</date> by andrea.breard</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Comments</head><p xml:id="CH8x4309-start"><seg corresp="#CH8x4309_CHANT_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-01-06T02:16:26.694+09:00">彭浩曰：「『楊』，校對人之姓，亦見於他簡，均位於簡末端下編線之下。本簡在『楊』前有一黑圓點，以示與題文區別」（頁39）。</seg><seg corresp="#CH8x4309_CHANT_001-1a.67" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-01-06T02:32:27.038+09:00">彭浩謂依文例，「一」下當有「也」字。然無礙文義，故不當脫文。下文諸句亦如是（頁41）。</seg><seg corresp="#CH8x4309_CHANT_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-01-06T03:01:50.951+09:00">「半」下二字殘缺，彭浩據下文補「分寸」。「半分寸」指一分寸的一半，即二十分之一寸（頁38-39）。</seg><seg corresp="#CH8x4309_CHANT_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#andrea.breard" modified="2023-01-06T03:02:19.316+09:00">Chinese comments by Peng Hao are based on 彭浩：《張家山漢簡〈算數書〉註釋》，北京：科學出版社，2001年.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>